title: Farm-to-Table
description: Farm-to-Table is an online platform connecting farmers directly with consumers to provide fresh produce. In this project, our team parodied our products with the theme of Plant Vs Zombies.

title: Elbi GenerosiTree
description: Elbi GenerosiTree is a mobile application developed using Flutter, designed to manage donations coming into the university. This project is a Flutter-based application aimed at streamlining the process of managing donations. It utilizes various packages and dependencies to offer a comprehensive and user-friendly experience.

title: Tamaan Mo Ko Beybe
description: Tamaan Mo Ko Beybe is a two-player game consisting of a throwing team and a dodger. The goal of the throwing team is to hit the dodger with the ball before the time runs out. The goal of the dodger is to dodge the ball until the time runs out.
